dict.string: Weird is wonderful in your eyes and you believe that the world is full of weirdoes. Let’s face it. Humans are pretty weird species. When we compare ourselves to other things in this world, we just add to the weird and wonderful parts of it. You like your egg scrambled and hate routine. Life is a rollercoaster for you and most people don’t understand your lifestyle and what you do as you have stepped out of your comfort zone and stepped into the weirdness.
Weird

You are as normal as normal gets-if there ever was such a thing! You wouldn’t miss a night without brushing your teeth or go a week without washing your bed sheets if your life depended on it. You love structure and routine and this is what keeps you on the right path. You can’t roll your tongue and you should be grateful that you have not been mixed with alien beings that make that ability possible. Being normal is by no means a bad thing; it just means you are part of select part of society and move along with it wherever life takes you.
Normal

You like to think you lead a normal life but something is quite off balance. You have strange habits and like obscure things. Your taste is refined and being obscure might be an understatement. People find it difficult to understand you and instead of following the crowd and eating fried eggs, or scrambled or dippy, you will go for poached-you like to go to the extreme of situations, try new things and look at things in a different perspective.
Obscure

Umm we're a little scared to say this but OK, here we go: You a total, 100% psychopath! You are not a very social person, you prefer being alone in your apartment, doing your own thing, with no intervention from the outside world. You are not a very empathic person, but you don't see that as a problem, you see that as an advantage! Our advice to you is to try to be more social (without kidnapping anyone), and see how you feel. You might like it!
100% psychopath!

You're a bit of a psycho :)Sometimes you are a little distant from other people. You are no stranger to difficult times and a little depression, but overall, you are fairly friendly, outgoing and enjoy the company of others. You don't like to be on your own too much, you are very empathic, and you do feel bad when you see someone in need (heck, you might even help others from time to time!)Don't worry about your potential to become a psychopath, as long as you keep yourself surrounded with good people and a healthy lifestyle, you will be fine!

You passed the psychopath test! You are a smart, assertive and dedicated person, but you are NOT a psychopath! You like to speak with other people, work, travel and learn. You don't feel caged in your daily life, and you are always there for others.
